    <h1>About Slop Bucket</h1>

    <p class="lead">Slop Bucket is the internet's most trusted source for information that feels true.</p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>Founded in 1997 by a group of former journalists who got tired of citing sources, Slop Bucket has been delivering content to screens worldwide for nearly three decades. Our mission is simple: give readers what they want to hear, formatted like the news they used to trust.</p>

    <h2>Our Values</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Confidence:</strong> We believe that saying something with enough conviction makes fact-checking unnecessary.</li>
        <li><strong>Speed:</strong> We publish first and verify never.</li>
        <li><strong>Engagement:</strong> If it makes you angry enough to share, we've done our job.</li>
        <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Our content is designed to be understood by anyone who already agrees with it.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our Team</h2>
    <p>Slop Bucket employs a rotating cast of thought leaders, wellness experts, anonymous sources, and behavioral economists who may or may not exist. All of our writers have credentials from institutions we're not authorized to name.</p>

